  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Once per <strong>Long</strong> <strong>Rest</strong>, you can spend <strong>3 AP</strong> to call on your deity to intervene on your behalf when your need is great to replenish you and your allies. </p><p>Make a <strong>DC 10 Spell Check</strong>. </p><p><strong>Success:</strong> You gain a pool of healing equal to twice your <strong>Prime</strong> <strong>Modifier</strong> that you can use to restore <strong>HP</strong> to any number of creatures within 5 Spaces, distributing the <strong>HP</strong> among them. </p><p>Additionally, you regain an amount of <strong>MP</strong> equal to your <strong>Prime</strong> <strong>Modifier</strong>. </p><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Your pool of healing is equal to your <strong>Prime</strong> <strong>Modifier</strong> and you only regain <strong>1 MP</strong>.</p>",
